 level in the iron-based\nsuperconductors must be explicitly accounted for in any attempt to understand\nthe mechanism of superconducting pairing in these materials.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 11 Jan 2016 23:19:28 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-01-13"}
