ergoing multiple interactions is\nprovided, which permits the modeling of a network of local systems in\nnonequilibrium at any spatial and temporal scale.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 12 Jan 2016 00:43:29 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-10-10"}
