he apparatus has been\ncontinuously running unattended for more than one week. The typical power\nspectrum sensitivity was a few $ 10^{-10} rad/s/\\sqrt(Hz)$, with integration\ntime not longer than tens of seconds. Improvements of the apparatus are ongoing\nin order to improve the integration time.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 12 Jan 2016 14:28:27 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 22 Jan 2016 17:05:22 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 29 Mar 2016 09:22:46 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-06-05"}
